@startuml
[*] --> WithdrawOptions: select amount from list of options
WithdrawOptions --> EnterCustomValue: enter custom value if different amount wanted
EnterCustomValue --> VerifyTransaction: verify transaction after entering amount
VerifyTransaction --> Reject : transaction rejected
Reject --> ReenterAmount: re-enter amount if transaction rejected
ReenterAmount --> VerifyTransaction: verify transaction again
@enduml
